    19ŌåÆ### Commits
    30ŌåÆ### Test Coverage
    31ŌåÆ
    32ŌåÆPull requests made against this repo will run `npm test` automatically.  Please make sure tests pass locally before submitting a PR.
    36ŌåÆ### Linting
    37ŌåÆ
    38ŌåÆLinting is also done automatically once tests pass.  `npm run lintfix` will fix most linting errors automatically.
    42ŌåÆ## What _not_ to contribute?
