    44ŌåÆ### Dependencies
    48ŌåÆ### Tools/Automation
    49ŌåÆ
    50ŌåÆOur core team is responsible for the maintenance of the tooling/automation in this project and we ask contributors to not make changes to these when contributing (e.g. `.github/*`, `.eslintrc.json`, `.licensee.json`).  Most of those files also have a header at the top to remind folks they are automatically generated.  Pull requests that alter these will not be accepted.
